      {id:"ji6",title:"Mecanum Drive Math",est:"20 min",content:`## Why Mecanum?
Mecanum wheels have 45-degree rollers that allow strafing sideways, forward, backward, and diagonal movement.

## The Formula
\`\`\`java
double y  = -gamepad1.left_stick_y;  // forward/back (negated)
double x  =  gamepad1.left_stick_x;  // strafe
double rx =  gamepad1.right_stick_x; // rotate

double frontLeft  = y + x + rx;
double frontRight = y - x - rx;
double backLeft   = y - x + rx;
double backRight  = y + x - rx;

// Normalize so no value exceeds 1.0
double maxPower = Math.max(Math.abs(frontLeft),
    Math.max(Math.abs(frontRight),
    Math.max(Math.abs(backLeft), Math.abs(backRight))));
if (maxPower > 1.0) {
    frontLeft /= maxPower; frontRight /= maxPower;
    backLeft  /= maxPower; backRight  /= maxPower;
}

leftFront.setPower(frontLeft);   rightFront.setPower(frontRight);
leftBack.setPower(backLeft);     rightBack.setPower(backRight);
