      {id:"sb3",title:"Game Piece Strategy",est:"14 min",content:`## Cycle Time — The Most Important Metric
A "cycle" = picking up a game piece and scoring it.

\`\`\`
Points per match ≈ Points per cycle × Cycles per match

4 pts/cycle × 15 cycles = 60 pts
6 pts/cycle × 8 cycles  = 48 pts
\`\`\`

Faster cycles often beat fewer high-value cycles!

## Prioritizing Scoring Zones
- High zones score more but are harder to reach
- Low zones are reliable but score less
- Maximize **consistent** scoring, not max per-cycle scoring`},
