      {id:"fa1",title:"Winning the FIRST Impact Award",est:"20 min",content:`## What is the Impact Award?
The Impact Award is the highest honor in FIRST — it recognizes the team with the greatest community impact. Winners advance to World Championship.

## Submission Components
1. Essay: narrative of your team's story and impact
2. Executive Summary: 10,000 characters max
3. Video: 4 minutes max
4. Presentation: 7 minutes plus Q&A to judges

