Controller Area Network — a 2-wire differential serial bus (CAN H + CAN L) that connects smart devices on FRC robots.

## FRC CAN Network
\`\`\`
roboRIO → PDH → TalonFX → SparkMax → SparkMax → ...
         ↑ 120Ω terminator at each end of bus
