Every device must have a unique ID (0–62). Set via:
- REV Hardware Client (Spark MAX, PDH)
- Phoenix Tuner X (Talon FX/SRX)
- CAN Configurator (other devices)

## Troubleshooting CAN Errors
\`\`\`
Common error patterns:
"CAN Bus Off" → wiring short or termination missing
"Receive Error" → bad cable, wrong ID, interference
"Bus Usage > 90%" → too many devices, reduce update rates
