      {id:"ji20",title:"Finite State Machine — Deep Dive",est:"25 min",content:`## FSM Architecture for Complex Robots

A well-designed FSM lets your robot handle complex behaviors without spaghetti code.

### Why FSM?
Compare these two approaches for scoring a game piece:

**Sequential (breaks easily):**
\`\`\`java
