1. **High mean, high variance**: Sometimes amazing, sometimes terrible — risky
2. **Broke down 2+ times in quals**: Will likely break in playoffs pressure
3. **All auto attempts failed**: May hurt alliance RP
4. **Pattern of penalties**: Will give RP to opponents in playoffs
