| Situation | Action |
|-----------|--------|
| Material caught in tool | Release grip, step back — let it spin free |
| Tool drops | Let it fall, don't catch |
| Injury | Stop tool, apply pressure, call for mentor |
| Fire | Use extinguisher (ABC type), call for help |
