          {type:"comment",label:"Mecanum Overview",code:`// Mecanum wheels have 45° rollers
// Combining power across 4 wheels enables:
// - Forward / Backward
// - Left / Right strafe
// - Rotation
// - Any combination simultaneously
//
// Each wheel power = drive ± strafe ± turn
// Wheel layout (looking down at robot):
