//   BL  BR`,explanation:"The magic of mecanum is that each wheel contributes differently to drive, strafe, and turn. The math combines all three inputs into four motor powers using simple addition and subtraction."},
          {type:"math",label:"The Mecanum Equation",code:`// Read driver inputs
double drive  = -gamepad1.left_stick_y;  // Forward/back
double strafe =  gamepad1.left_stick_x;  // Left/right
double turn   =  gamepad1.right_stick_x; // Rotation

// Calculate wheel powers
double fl = drive + strafe + turn;  // Front-Left
double fr = drive - strafe - turn;  // Front-Right
double bl = drive - strafe + turn;  // Back-Left
double br = drive + strafe - turn;  // Back-Right`,explanation:"The signs follow from the 45° roller directions. FL and BR share the same strafe sign (+). FR and BL share the opposite (-). The turn term adds to left wheels and subtracts from right wheels (or vice versa for left turn). Memorize this table!"},
