  High Goal:     5 pts × max 12/match = 60 pts
  Low Goal:      2 pts × max 8/match  = 16 pts
  Endgame Climb: 20 pts
  Auto Bonus:    10 pts
  ─────────────────────────────────────────
  Theoretical max = 106 pts per alliance

  Realistic target (3 good robots): ~65 pts
