// Add debug output at key points
telemetry.addData("=== MOTOR TEST ===", "");
telemetry.addData("Power commanded", motor.getPower());
telemetry.addData("Encoder position", motor.getCurrentPosition());
telemetry.addData("Motor controller", motor.getController().toString());
telemetry.update();
\`\`\`

### Wire Continuity Test
If you suspect a broken wire:
1. Power OFF the robot completely
2. Use a multimeter in continuity mode
3. Touch probes to both ends of the wire
4. Beep = connected ✓ | Silence = break in wire ✗
