      {id:"pya6",title:"Building a Live Scouting API",est:"35 min",content:`## Flask + WebSockets for Real-Time Scouting

Build a system where scouts on phones submit data that instantly appears on a strategy screen.

### Architecture
\`\`\`
Phone Scout → POST /api/submit → Flask Server → Push to Strategy Screen
                                              → Store to JSON file
