    .onTrue(Commands.runOnce(() -> shooter.stop(), shooter));`,explanation:"whileTrue runs the command while the button is held and cancels it on release. onTrue starts the command on button press and doesn't cancel when released. Commands.runOnce() creates a one-shot command inline — no separate class needed for simple actions."},
