      {id:"sb11",title:"Reading the Game Manual",est:"20 min",content:`## How to Read a FIRST Game Manual

Every FIRST season starts with a game manual. Reading it correctly saves hours of penalty trouble.

### Manual Structure (FRC)
\`\`\`
Section 1: Introduction & Dates
Section 2: Game Overview (READ THIS FIRST)
