      {id:"pi13",title:"Discord Bot for FRC Scouting Alerts",est:"30 min",content:`## Build a Discord Bot for Your Team

A Discord bot can auto-post match schedules, TBA updates, and scouting alerts to your team channel.

### Setup
\`\`\`bash
pip install discord.py requests python-dotenv
\`\`\`

Create a \`.env\` file:
\`\`\`
DISCORD_TOKEN=your_bot_token_here
TBA_KEY=your_tba_api_key
